game.name: Jack Propose Marriage Elsa
game.description:
Oh, what a lovely moment is about to come in the life of Queen Elsa! Yes, Jack Frost fell in love with her and he has decided to propose her love now. He has a plan for a wonderful wedding proposal, but he seeks for a little bit of guidance from you as it is the first time the prince is going to propose a beautiful girl. Join Jack Propose Marriage Elsa and be prepared to help him pick up a nice outfit! Make sure to arrange everything he needs for a picnic. 
There are plenty of things to choose from a wide collection of colorful shirts, and fancy pants combined with a matching pair of sporty shoes. More you play with the outfit and necessary options, the easier it will become for you to finalize a wonderful outfit. Try to challenge your designer abilities to the optimum possible level to dress him up for this most awaited occasion in this brand new dressing game for girls! A new hairstyle can make a difference when it comes to making his picnic a more romantic. 
Choose a nice picnic blanket and arrange all the items including various delicious items in this girls game! Make sure to make their celebration remarkable one with the selection of some champagne.  Do not forget to write the romantic 2 words she wants to listen deliberately! Get ready to play the role of wedding planner and help Elsa to attain a bridal look and Jack to get a super elegant groom outfit! All the best to help them to find a perfect wedding look in this wedding game!
